                  </hi>. I am assistant to Mr. Cockburn, pawnbroker, of Rich<lb></lb>mond. I produce a silk gown, pledged on 7th July by the prisoner—I gave him the duplicate produced.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18510818-name-1005" type="witnessName">
